file: crates/ctx-verify/tests/checks.rs
purpose: Behavioral tests for ctx-verify parsers and orchestration logic using a fake Runner. No real processes are spawned; all tool output is canned strings.
invariants:
  - FakeRunner returns ToolMissing for any key absent from by_first_arg.
external_deps:
  - ctx_verify: crate under test (checks, error, model, parse, runner modules).
  - serde_json: verifies serialization shape of CheckReport/Report.
functions: